{"tid":2296060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：5千元肺炎確診奬金只適用於措施生效後本地確診者","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T11:47:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":69,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"1b483b7f472837808a3183c312d059396dfc77e0","tid":2296060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561307-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561307-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=93df11b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561307-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3b68cbe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561307-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府將會為新型肺炎確診患者提供一筆過5000元津貼，細節待勞工及福利局敲定後公布。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，初步計劃是為接受檢測屬本地感染的確診者提供有關津貼，即經強制檢測後確診或特定檢測群組的人士，或自願檢測後的確診者，都可獲津貼，毋須作經資產審查，以避免繁複行政程序，不過津貼只適用於措施生效後的本地感染確診者。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始今早接受傳媒訪問時說，部分人尤其基層市民對強制檢測可能會卻步，擔心確診後會影響生計，因此當局會為確診者提供一筆過5000元津貼，勞福局定出細節後會盡快公布。"},{"pid":"8dc7bbe1155e38b8cbbdb2a15c19448a577789e8","tid":2296060,"uid":77717,"like":149,"dislike":0,"score":149,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"are you ready guys?"},{"pid":"bc1eaefb027f20ae8b7a349bdce06a759393e0aa","tid":2296060,"uid":57308,"like":147,"dislike":2,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"確診獎金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e287fab19374f6780b9b1437ab1ace163d2179","tid":2296060,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:44:5